down", "html": "<p>When granting permission to a resource \"gzserver\" that does not exist, the message is:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-python\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;hugo@osrfoundation.org&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">has</span> <span class=\"n\">insufficient</span> <span class=\"n\">priviledges</span> <span class=\"n\">to</span> <span class=\"n\">manage</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Bob&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">access</span> <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;gzserver&quot;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>But it would be better if it was something like: the resource does not exist.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-06-02T20:12:17.237430+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-06-02T20:12:17.237430+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1}